        keyRules:["Subjunctive: WEIRDO — Wishes, Emotion, Impersonal expressions, Recommendations/Requests, Doubt/Denial, Ojala. Use indicative for facts and certainty.","Preterite: completed action with clear beginning/end (Ayer comí una pizza). Imperfect: habitual past (De niño comía pizza todos los viernes), ongoing state (Estaba cansado).","Ser: identity, characteristics, origin, time, passive voice, what something is. Estar: location, temporary states, conditions, emotions, progressive tense.","Por: cause/reason (Gracias por tu ayuda), duration (Estudié por tres horas), exchange (Lo compré por diez dólares). Para: purpose (Estudio para aprender), deadline (Lo necesito para el lunes)."],
