        keyRules:["Connect all 6 pictures — AP Chinese story narration requires a complete narrative arc, not 6 separate descriptions. Each picture should logically lead to the next.","Express inner life: 'The person stood at the door' (低分) vs '他站在门口，心里既紧张又期待，不知道接下来会发生什么' (高分). Adding thoughts and emotions elevates the score.","Logical causation: use 因为…所以, 由于…因此, 正是因为…才 to show cause-and-effect connections between events.","Conclusion with reflection: the best stories end with the character learning something or the situation having broader significance — 从这件事中，他们意识到了…"],
